## § PLATFORM CONTEXT

**Company:** EU medtech startup · Non-invasive regenerative technology
**Modalities:** Oxygen (mHBOT) · Hydrogen (inhalation, water) · Light (RLT, NIR) · Signal (PEMF, VNS)
**Brand:** Premium · Scientific · Accessible · "Where mind connects with matter"
**Model:** Rental-first (€150–600/mo) → Purchase → B2B clinics
**Customer:** 35–65yo EU professional · Evidence-oriented · Quality investor
**Markets:** EU-first (en, de, pl, nl) · GDPR · MDR 2017/745

**Stack:**
- Main app: Next.js 16 + React 19.2 + TypeScript 5 strict (App Router, server-first hybrid)
- Turbopack: default bundler in v16 (no --turbopack flag needed)
- React Compiler: stable in v16 (automatic memoization, `reactCompiler: true` in config)
- Control panel: Next.js 16 + React 18 (separate workspace `control-panel/` — different React version, NEVER cross-import components/types, communicate via API only)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS v4 (CSS-first config — NO tailwind.config.js, @theme in globals.css)
- Linting/Formatting: Biome ONLY (no ESLint, no Prettier)
- Database: Drizzle ORM + Neon (serverless PostgreSQL) — NO Prisma
- Cache/Queue: Upstash Redis (cache + queue ONLY, NOT rate limiting)
- Auth: Auth.js v5 (next-auth@beta, self-hosted, Drizzle adapter)
- Server Actions: next-safe-action OR ZSA (evaluate, document decision)
- URL State: nuqs v2
- Forms: react-hook-form + zod
- Client Data: @tanstack/react-query (realtime/polling only)
- Client State: Zustand
- Env Validation: @t3-oss/env-nextjs + Zod (ALL env vars through lib/env.ts)
- Email: React Email + Resend (NO nodemailer)
- File Uploads: Uploadthing
- Background Jobs: Trigger.dev v3 OR Inngest
- Security: Arcjet (bot protection, rate limiting, email validation, DDOS)
- Product Analytics: PostHog EU (session replay, feature flags, funnels)
- Web Analytics: @vercel/analytics (supplementary)
- Speed Metrics: @vercel/speed-insights
- Error Monitoring: @sentry/nextjs (EU DSN — ingest.de.sentry.io)
- SEO: schema-dts + next-sitemap
- Animation: motion (from 'motion/react') + @formkit/auto-animate (lists)
- Image Optimization: sharp
- Bundle Analysis: @next/bundle-analyzer + Knip (unused code detection)
- Payments: Stripe
- Testing: Vitest + Playwright + @axe-core/playwright (a11y)
- Security Scanning: Semgrep for static analysis
- Deploy: Vercel

**Commands:**
`pnpm dev` (next dev — Turbopack default) · `pnpm build` (next build) · `pnpm start` (next start) · `pnpm test` (vitest) · `pnpm check` (biome check + build + test) · `pnpm analyze` (bundle analysis) · `pnpm knip` (unused code) · `pnpm db:generate` (drizzle-kit generate) · `pnpm db:migrate` (drizzle-kit migrate) · `pnpm db:studio` (drizzle-kit studio) · `pnpm email:dev` (react-email dev)

