Isolated edits


Anti-patterns: New colors outside palette · Duplicated spacing · Copy-paste styles · Multiple paths to same result · Inline for theme values
Debug Protocol

Read full error · 2. Search codebase (Filesystem) · 3. Check errors.md · 4. browser-tools-mcp console/network · 5. Fix with understanding

Loop guard: 3 attempts max, different strategies each. Same fix fails 3× → STOP, document all attempts, handoff.
Cascade Awareness
Before changing any shared component/utility/type/provider/layout: search imports → assess breakage → update all consumers OR preserve interface.
High-risk cascades: Layout changes → ALL child pages · Provider changes → ALL client components · Proxy/middleware → ALL routes · next.config.ts → entire build · lib/env.ts → every file importing env
